\v 24 Lezi ezine zingezincinyane zomhlaba, kanti zihlakaniphile zenziwe zihlakaniphe:
\v 25 Ubunyonyo buyisizwe esingelamandla\x + 6.6.\x*, kanti bulungisa ukudla kwabo ehlobo\x + 6.8.\x*.
\v 26 Imbila ziyisizwe esingelamandla\x + Hlab. 104.18.\x*\x + Levi 11.5.\x*, kanti zimisa indlu yazo edwaleni\x + Hlab. 104.18.\x*.
\v 27 Intethe kazilankosi\x + 6.7.\x*, kanti zonke ziphuma zehlukene \add ngamaviyo\x + Jow. 2.25.\x*\add*.
\v 28 Umbankwa ubambelela ngezandla ezimbili, njalo usezigodlweni zenkosi.
